                LOOKAHEAD(3) result=IsBooleanExpression(left)
                |
                LOOKAHEAD(3) result=IsUnknownExpression(left)
                |
                LOOKAHEAD(2) result=LikeExpression(left)
                |
                LOOKAHEAD(3) result=IsDistinctExpression(left)
                |
                result=SimilarToExpression(left)
